---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Aminu Abdusalam" description="A bit about me.">
  <section class="container container-narrow prose">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      I'm a Product Manager at Microsoft on the Xbox Consumer Commerce team, an ex-engineer,
      and a builder who can't stop tinkering.
    </p>

    <p>
      I grew up in Nigeria, moved to the U.S. for college at <strong>Fisk University</strong>
      (Nashville, TN), where I studied Computer Science and helped lead our team through the
      NFL Battle of the Brains. From there I did a dual-degree program at <strong>Vanderbilt
      University</strong>, added a second CS degree, and started my career as a software
      engineer.
    </p>

    <p>
      Today I own subscription commerce surfaces at Xbox — things like device warranty
      subscriptions, Ubisoft Classics inside Game Pass, and the Ask-to-Subscribe experience
      that lets kids get parental approval before checkout. I've been promoted three times
      in three years (L59 → L62), which mostly means I've learned to ship things and
      write clearly.
    </p>

    <h2>Timeline</h2>
    <ul class="timeline">
      <li>
        <span class="year">2026</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Product Manager 2, Microsoft Xbox</strong>
          <p>Xbox Consumer Commerce — Warranty Subs, Ubisoft Classics, Ask-to-Subscribe.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="year">2023</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Product Manager, Microsoft Xbox</strong>
          <p>Started on Consumer Commerce, first shipped experiences for hundreds of millions of gamers.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="year">2023</span>
        <div>
          <strong>B.E. Computer Science, Vanderbilt University</strong>
          <p>Dual-degree program with Fisk. Software engineering, systems, and a lot of coffee.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="year">2021</span>
        <div>
          <strong>B.S. Computer Science, Fisk University</strong>
          <p>Nashville, TN. NFL Battle of the Brains team. Learned how to build in public.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What I'm into</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Subscription and marketplace commerce (payments, entitlements, tax, fraud)</li>
      <li>AI agents that actually change how PMs work day-to-day</li>
      <li>Fantasy football (currently commissioner, currently losing)</li>
      <li>Writing about the messy in-between of product and engineering</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="cta-line">
      <a href="mailto:aminuabdusalam2019@gmail.com">Say hi →</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    padding-block: var(--space-10) var(--space-8);
  }
  .prose h1 {
    font-size: var(--fs-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .prose h2::before {
    content: '## ';
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .prose .lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--color-text-strong);
  }
  .prose ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }
  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
  }
  .timeline li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    padding: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px;
    top: var(--space-6);
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--color-accent-glow);
  }
  .year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    min-width: 60px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .timeline strong {
    color: var(--color-text-strong);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }
  .timeline p {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-line {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
</style>
